# Jenkins #
## Configure Maven ##
1. Install Maven in Server
	1. [Maven Download Page](https://maven.apache.org/download.cgi)
	2. Download [apache-maven-3.5.0-bin.tar.gz](http://mirror.fibergrid.in/apache/maven/maven-3/3.5.0/binaries/apache-maven-3.5.0-bin.tar.gz)
	3. Click on **Manage Jenkins**
	4. Click on **Global Tool Configuration**
	5. Click on **Maven installations** under **Maven**
	6. Enter the following details:
		1. Name: Maven
		2. MAVEN_HOME: `/home/am/Documents/Softwares/apache-maven-3.5.0`
		3. Uncheck **Install automatically** option
	7. Click **Save**
2. New project with Maven:
	1. Click **New Item**
	2. Select **Maven project**